caption:
Who are the people that you spend the most time with?

Are you all in the same financial bracket?

Are you at the same level in your careers?

Do you live in the same communities, spend your time doing similar things, frequent the same spaces?

Now…are you trying to achieve something different?

Then think about diversifying your community.

Include people who have achieved the things that you are aiming for.

Folks who are an example of what you desire to achieve. 

Everybody needs a role model!
